data.name: ContentInfoAttribute
desc: These are the possible values for ContentInfo.Attributes.

items.name: INSERT_WITH_INPUTSTREAM
lines: Supply an input stream with the InsertCommandArgument, when committing the new content by executing the command \"insert\" at it.

items.name: KIND_DOCUMENT
lines: The new content is of kind document.
It's value for the property \"IsDocument\" will be true.

items.name: KIND_FOLDER
lines: The new content is of kind folder.
It's value for the property \"IsFolder\" will be true.

items.name: KIND_LINK
lines: The new content is of kind link.
It will support the property \"TargetURL\" ( which identifies it as a link ).
